article.headline: Wolf helps Yale hold off Cornell 80-78 for 10th straight victory

images.name: Knowling's Late Basket Gives Yale 80-78 Win Over Cornell  - Via Ivy League
images.caption: Matt Knowling hit the game-winner with 3.2 seconds remaining to improve Yale's record to 7-0 in league play

article.linkText: Wolf helps Yale hold off Cornell 80-78 for 10th straight victory
article.story: NEW HAVEN, Conn. -- — Danny Wolf totaled 25 points and 10 rebounds to help Yale hold off Cornell 80-78 on Saturday for its 10th win in a row. Wolf made 10 of 17 shots with a 3-pointer for the Bulldogs (16-6, 7-0 Ivy League). John Poulakidas scored 13 points. Matt Knowling pitched in with 12 points and nine rebounds. Chris Manon finished with 22 points to pace the Big Red (17-4, 6-1), who saw a seven-game win streak end. Nazir Williams added 17 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
